@page
@model Web.Pages.Admin.IndexModel
@{
    Layout = null;
    ViewData["Admin"] = "管理页面";
}
@* 把blazor中的index页面移到这里来，并且把原来的index页面删除掉。配置好id即可 。并把Layout清空，否则页面会冲突*@
@* 这里引用的是blazor中的根文件 *@
<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
    <meta charset="utf-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <title>BlazorAdmin</title>
    <base href="/" />
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="lib/bootstrap/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css" />
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="css/app.css" />
    <link rel="icon" type="image/png" href="favicon.png" />
    <link href="BlazorAdmin.styles.css" rel="stylesheet" />
    <link href="manifest.webmanifest" rel="manifest" />
    <link rel="apple-touch-icon" sizes="512x512" href="icon-512.png" />
    <link rel="apple-touch-icon" sizes="192x192" href="icon-192.png" />
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/admin.css" />   @* css会有缓存，记得Ctrl+F5刷新浏览器 *@

</head>

<body>
    <div id="admin">
        <svg class="loading-progress">
            <circle r="40%" cx="50%" cy="50%" />
            <circle r="40%" cx="50%" cy="50%" />
        </svg>
        <div class="loading-progress-text"></div>
    </div>

    <div id="blazor-error-ui">
        An unhandled error has occurred.
        <a href="." class="reload">Reload</a>
        <span class="dismiss">🗙</span>
    </div>
    @* admin.js直接写在BlazorAdmin中就行，但是要设置admin.js的属性(复制到输出目录=>始终复制)，否则在bin\debug中的wwwroot文件夹中找不到admin.js。导致路径错误*@
    <script src="/js/admin.js"></script>
    <script src="_framework/blazor.webassembly.js"></script>
</body>
</html>
